== 20世紀以後火山活動 ==
'''Anak Krakatau'''（"喀拉喀托之子"）是1927年6月才冒出海面的[[火山島|火山島]]。最初該島被海浪的力量所拍打削平，但最終火山的生長速度超過了海浪的侵蝕速度。1930年8月，喀拉喀托之子終於成為永久島嶼，自那以後一直是火山學家研究火山島形成的對象。自1950年代開始，該火山島以每星期約13公分的速率持續增高中。

2018年12月22日，該火山再次噴發，[[2018年巽他海峡海啸|並造成海嘯]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/12/22/indonesia-tsunami-least-20-dead-165-injured-waves-hit-beaches/|title=Indonesia 'volcano tsunami': At least 168 dead and 745 injured after Krakatoa erupts|last=|first=|date=23 December 2018|website=telegraph.co.uk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816002254/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/12/22/indonesia-tsunami-least-20-dead-165-injured-waves-hit-beaches/|archive-date=2019-08-16|dead-url=no|access-date=23 December 2018}}</ref>。截至12月24日，已造成430人死亡，1400多人傷，150人失蹤<ref name="BBC_Dec24">{{cite web |last1=Amos |first1=Jonathan |title=Indonesia tsunami: Death toll from Anak Krakatau volcano rises |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-46674490 |website=BBC News |date=24 December 2018 |accessdate=2018-12-30 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094723/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-46674490 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據《[[衛報|衛報]]》報道，海嘯造成{{tsl|en|Submarine landslide|海底山體滑坡}}<ref name=Guardian2018-12-23a>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/dec/22/multiple-fatalities-as-tsunami-hits-beaches-in-indonesia|title=Sunda Strait tsunami death toll likely to rise, say Indonesian officials|author1=Justin McCurry|author2=Frances Perraudin|author3=agencies|authorlink3=News agency|publisher=''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]''|accessdate=23 December 2018|date=23 December 2018|quote=The tsunami is believed to have been caused by undersea landslides that followed an eruption of the Anak Krakatau volcano. There were no significant seismic tremors to indicate a tsunami was coming.|archive-date=2019-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105185222/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/dec/22/multiple-fatalities-as-tsunami-hits-beaches-in-indonesia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月23日，分析衛星圖像和直昇機拍得的影像後發現火山西南麓連同山峰發生了[[山崩|山崩]]，沉入海中，造成海嘯<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.volcanodiscovery.com/krakatoa/2018/dec/eruption-tsunami/updates.html |title=22-23 Dec 2018 eruption & tsunami of Krakatoa - updates |publisher=[[Volcano_Discovery|Volcano Discovery]] |date=25 December 2018 |accessdate=26 December 2018 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609182341/https://www.volcanodiscovery.com/krakatoa/2018/dec/eruption-tsunami/updates.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2656002/print |title=印尼海嘯後…1張圖看出火山崩塌、沉入海中 |date=2018-12-28 |work=自由時報 |accessdate=2018-12-30 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807122138/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2656002/print |dead-url=no }}</ref>，火山因此失去了其三分之二的水面上高度和體積，餘下大約{{cvt|110|m|||}}高<ref name="bbc1229">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-46707731|title=Indonesian volcano's lost stature|last=Amos|first=Jonathan|date=2018-12-29|work=BBC News|access-date=2018-12-29|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202125257/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-46707731|dead-url=no}}</ref>，體積縮減1.5億至1.8億立方公尺，只餘下4000萬至7000萬立方公尺左右<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1936783-國際-印尼火山崩塌+體積大縮三分二+海嘯風險減 |title=印尼火山崩塌 體積大縮三分二 海嘯風險減 |date=2018-12-30 |work=星島日報 |accessdate=2022-03-16 |archive-date=2019-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708235621/http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1936783-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E7%81%AB%E5%B1%B1%E5%B4%A9%E5%A1%8C+%E9%AB%94%E7%A9%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%B8%AE%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%BA%8C+%E6%B5%B7%E5%98%AF%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E6%B8%9B |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年4月10日晚上10时左右，喀拉喀托火山发生喷发<ref>{{cite news |title=印尼喀拉喀托之子火山深夜喷发 |url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20200411-1044755 |accessdate=2020-04-12 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820212932/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20200411-1044755 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

